'''Health care''' is the preservation of [[mental health|mental]] and physical [[health]] by preventing or treating [[illness]]es through services offered by the health profession and its staff. Health care includes all reasonable and necessary medical aid, medical examinations, medical [[treatment]]s, medical diagnoses, medical evaluations and medical services. The right to health care is considered one of [[human rights]] with [[international human rights law]] as well as [[social security]].

